Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.29,0:00:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在煤矿中战斗一周后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.04,0:00:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾获得了大量技能和本领甚至让我懒得去数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.64,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我大意了受到了伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.15,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.16,0:00:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪潮即将来临我们该换装备了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀刮目相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成大美女了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近都没见你们干什么去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请旅店的人教了我餐桌礼仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想像尚文大人那样优雅地用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了和之前那个小不点不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.08,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥你是木头人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.42,0:03:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很惊讶这个国家居然全民萝莉控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘真可爱再送你一根吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白小女孩可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可每个人都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.32,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥你不知道吗亚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些了今天我们是来给尚文大人买防具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有推荐的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢今天是为了买你的装备…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.42,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此很感激不过请先考虑您自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您忘记自己在草原上受伤的事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不还是该买你的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人开玩笑也得有个分寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔这把剑看起来很锋利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法铁打的剑要试试吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以算便宜一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是小姑娘的请求我就打个折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个能再看看盔甲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该说她变得难缠了还是该说她脸皮变厚了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预算大概是180枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件盔甲怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确这样就没有尚文大人的特点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也可以帮小哥定做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯用手头上的素材现做明天之前能做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,务必拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了剑给我们打折了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器屋老板是个好人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才不是我的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.13,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我最便宜的套餐她要儿童套餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.84,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚尚文大人我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要最便宜的套餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强自己装成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来太像坏人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合很帅气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其名为蛮族之铠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺帅的像盗贼一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹是勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易做好不装备就亏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城镇的氛围越来越严肃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟浪潮快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.44,0:06:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果至少能知道什么时候在哪出现就可以研究对策了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了没人告诉小哥你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城镇的广场上能看到的教会里有个大沙漏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个沙漏漏光时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.04,0:06:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者会和同伴一起被传送到发生浪潮的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.22,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是国王提到的龙刻沙漏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它显示了浪潮到来的倒计时吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的人是尚文吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还穿着这种装备战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人这几位是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等元康大人在和你说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.69,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是枪之勇者北村元康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.99,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康大人您对区区亚人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么可爱的女孩不适合拿剑我来保护你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.92,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我决定和尚文大人一起战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和尚文?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.59,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行你和这种人在一起会有危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛我没说错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.23,0:08:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也听过尚文的传闻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.07,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪潮时再见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拖我们的后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.17,0:08:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您和其他勇者大人之间发生了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去休息了晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.53,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我说出真相也不会有人相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.02,0:09:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那个我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸自己遇到了尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.36,0:09:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人治好了我的病给我热热的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我如何生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母回不来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以防止别的孩子遭遇同样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.42,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且给了我战斗的理由对抗浪潮的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是您的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会跟随您到天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.36,0:10:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.39,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾厄的浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.92,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲁特村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民的避难…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烽火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知骑士团具体地点就撒手不管了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.52,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然城堡离这里不远但等骑士团赶到村子就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.36,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去鲁特村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.07,0:11:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅你去引导居民避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.01,0:12:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人您呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吸引敌人的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.32,0:12:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听好趁我吸引敌人的时候赶紧去避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边丧尸们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会拼命保护陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也真是笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这数量实在应付不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把村庄的损失控制到最小…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.63,0:14:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有消退的迹象他们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.01,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.02,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家目睹了勇者大人的英姿重新想过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.19,0:15:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的村庄不能逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.82,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了避难完成前帮忙维持战线吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们打不过它退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有家人吧别白白死在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.61,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我们你们快去避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是请一定要平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.42,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人数量根本没有减少怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.18,0:16:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口气烧死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者吗挺耐打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.37,0:16:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切打算把我们一起烧死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道尚文大人在还放火我会根据你的回答决定杀不杀你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.85,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者的同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是尚文大人的剑不许你们无礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.23,0:17:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区亚人想违抗王国骑士团吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.11,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管自己必须保护的人民什么骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.28,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.37,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错老老实实待着我们也不会打错人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实看着你们变成魔物的食物或许也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌重新排阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要光荣战死在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.98,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了我们来争取时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间你们重新排阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.45,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.24,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.01,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给盾之勇者我们前往三勇者身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护盾之勇者密集阵型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密集阵型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给它最后一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.75,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招闪电枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人天空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.19,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的B0SS很好打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.44,0:19:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯这样的话下一波浪潮也是小菜一碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了尚文呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.41,0:19:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来是对的来了只会拖后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.49,0:19:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士团吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在来也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.34,0:19:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这么说国王准备了报酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的魔物全都打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.73,0:20:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有盾之勇者大人我们就要死在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过是顺势而为吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.37,0:21:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有您在我们才能活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会忘记您的恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被感谢了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.52,0:21:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我一样的人应该减少一些了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.58,0:21:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了很多魔物
